@startuml uml_class_messaging
title LLD — messaging-service (HTTP + gRPC — proto/messaging.proto)
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica

package "HTTP / gRPC transport" {
  class "Express API\n(server.ts)" as Http <<Node>>
  class "MessagingService\n(grpc-server.ts)" as Grpc <<Node>> {
    Forum: posts, comments, votes
    DMs: send, thread, read receipts
    HealthCheck()
    --
    see proto/messaging.proto
  }
}

package "Domain (Prisma)" {
  class Message <<entity>>
  class Post <<entity>>
  class Comment <<entity>>
  class Group <<entity>>
  class MessageRead <<entity>>
}

package "Infrastructure" {
  class "PrismaClient" as Prisma <<ORM>>
  class "Kafka emitters\n(messaging.events)" as K <<service>>
}

Http --> Prisma
Grpc --> Prisma
Http --> K
Grpc --> K
Prisma ..> Message
Post --> Comment : contains
Group --> Message : channels

note bottom of Grpc
  **Full RPC surface:** `proto/messaging.proto`
  (MessagingService — 20+ methods).
  **Events:** `proto/events/messaging/…`
  for immutable Kafka payloads.
end note

@enduml
